    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1890-06-23T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1890-06-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="17"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d17">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Mizner</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1890-06-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 23, 1890</date>. (Received June
                        24.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Mizner informs Mr. Blaine of the credited report in Guatemala of a successful
                    revolution in Salvador on the night of the 22d instant, during which the
                    President and others were assassinated.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
